name: Glossier
description: Elevate your skincare routine with Glossier's essential beauty collection. This curated set includes six must-have products designed to cleanse, exfoliate, hydrate, protect, and enhance your natural beauty.

name: Curology Essential Skincare Trio
description: Discover the simplicity of personalized skincare with Curologys essential trio, designed to cater to your unique skin needs.

name: CocoOil - Body Oil
description: Indulge in the luxurious hydration of CocoOil Body Oil, crafted with 100% organic coconut oil to nourish and rejuvenate your skin. This minimalist, sleek white bottle contains a rich formula that absorbs quickly, leaving your skin feeling soft and radiant without any greasy residue.

name: Mad About Waves and Curls
description: Embrace your natural texture with Schwarzkopf Professional's Mad About Waves & Curls Collection. This set includes four expertly formulated products designed to enhance and define your waves and curls, providing the care and styling support your hair needs.

name: Luxurious Skincare Collection by Cousin
description: Indulge in the ultimate skincare experience with Cousin's premium collection, designed to elevate your beauty routine with elegance and efficacy. This set includes four meticulously crafted products, each housed in sleek black packaging with gold accents, exuding sophistication and luxury.
